Sensor Pie._queryString: select Monitored, New, Warning, Predictive from Sensorlist

SensorList._queryString:
{[p]
 select SensorID, Temperature, (Temperature%(max Temperature))*100, Conductivity, (Conductivity%(max Conductivity))*100, Ozone, (Ozone%(max Ozone))*100, Flow, (Flow%(max Flow))*100, ComboI, (ComboI%(max ComboI))*100, TemperatureID,OzoneID,	FlowID,	ConductivityID, Location, Batch
 from Sensorlist where Plant = p
 
 }

PlantStatus._queryString: select Plant, TimeInProduction, EnergyConsumed, ProductProduced, EnergyCost, PlantRevenueDay, PerEfficiency, NumberofSensors, SensorAlerts, TimeChg, EnergyChg, ProductChg, EnergyCostChg, PlantRevChg, SensorAlertChg, (SensorAlerts % (max SensorAlerts))*100 from Plantstatus

PlantLocations._queryString: select  Plant, Lat, Long, EnergyConsumed, ProductProduced, EnergyCost, PlantRevenueDay, PerEfficiency, NumberofSensors from Plantstatus

getSensorHistory._queryString:
{[p]


 
  select ID, Location, Batch,
  `$"," vs' string New_Alerts,
  `$"," vs' string Temperature,
  `$"," vs' string Flow,
  `$"," vs' string Conductivity,
  `$"," vs' string Ozone,
  `$"," vs' string Combo_Change
  from  CIPSHistData where Plant = p}
